OL,3,CAround 2,500 homes must still 'boil
OL,4,Cwater' over parasite risk
OL,6,FThousands of Devon residents must
OL,7,Fcontinue to boil their tap water
OL,8,Fbefore drinking it because of a
OL,9,Fparasite outbreak, a water company has
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FIt comes after 46 confirmed cases of
OL,13,Fcryptosporidiosis - a waterborne
OL,14,Fillness which can cause unpleasant
OL,15,Fsymptoms such as diarrhoea and
OL,16,Fvomiting.
OL,18,FAround 2,500 households in Brixham,
OL,19,Fsouth Devon, have been told their tap
OL,20,Fwater could still be unsafe to drink.
