OL,6,FThe microscopic cryptosporidium
OL,7,Fparasite, which caused the disease,
OL,8,Flikely entered the water network
OL,9,Fthrough a damaged air pipe in a field
OL,10,Fcontaining cattle.
OL,12,FAround 17,000 households and
OL,13,Fbusinesses were issued with a 'boil
OL,14,Fwater' notice on Wednesday.
OL,16,FSouth West Water (SWW) has said 14,500
OL,17,Fhouseholds can now safely drink tap
OL,18,Fwater again, but around 2,500 homes
OL,19,Fmust continue to boil their water.
