OL,6,FThe 'boil water' notice remains in
OL,7,Fplace while work is undertaken to
OL,8,Frefill the Hillhead reservoir.
OL,10,FDavid Harris, drought and resilience
OL,11,Fdirector at SWW, said: "The Hillhead
OL,12,Freservoir has been successfully
OL,13,Fdrained, thoroughly cleaned, and we
OL,14,Fwill start refilling today.
OL,16,F"We will also start flushing the wider
OL,17,FHillhead network today, which is being
OL,18,Fcontinuously monitored as we work to
OL,19,Feliminate any traces of
OL,20,Fcryptosporidium.
