OL,6,F"We will not lift the boil water
OL,7,Fnotice in Hillhead until we and our
OL,8,Fpublic health partners are completely
OL,9,Fsatisfied it is safe to do so.
OL,11,F"I want to again apologise for the
OL,12,Fimmense disruption this is causing.
OL,13,FThis should not have happened and I
OL,14,Fpromise we will fix this problem as
OL,15,Fsoon as possible."
OL,17,FSWW said an additional #100
OL,18,Fcompensation will be paid to customers
OL,19,Fin the areas which continue to be
OL,20,Faffected ` bringing the total to #215.
