OL,6,FThree stations continue to offer safe
OL,7,Fbottled water to customers alongside
OL,8,Fdirect deliveries to vulnerable
OL,9,Fcustomers, schools, hospitals and care
OL,10,Fhomes.
OL,12,FConservative MP Anthony Mangnall,
OL,13,Fwhose Totnes constituency includes
OL,14,FBrixham, had previously told the PA
OL,15,Fnews agency that SWW's response to the
OL,16,Foutbreak was "contemptible and just
OL,17,Fgenerally incompetent".
