OL,6,FThe company said affected residents
OL,7,Fcan continue to use their tap water as
OL,8,Fnormal for washing, bathing and
OL,9,Fflushing the toilet.
OL,11,FThe disease can be picked up directly
OL,12,Ffrom the faeces of another person or
OL,13,Fanimal, from swimming in or drinking
OL,14,Fcontaminated water, or by eating
OL,15,Fcontaminated food such as unwashed
OL,16,Fvegetables.
OL,18,FThe number of confirmed cases could
OL,19,Frise because of a delay in symptom
OL,20,Fdevelopment caused by the parasite's
OL,21,Fincubation period.
